Cleveland Bar Association v. Clower.

[Cite as Cleveland Bar Assn. v. Clower (1989), 41 Ohio St. 3d 601.]

(No. D.D. 88-28 Submitted January 11, 1989 Decided February 8, 1989.)

James K. Clower is publicly reprimanded.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
